: center;\">2017-9-30 12:46am-10:46pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/a09GUCK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa09GUCK.png&h=423467c8&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kXWjbxb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkXWjbxb.png&h=88ea7795&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(2)陳法拉vs莊錠欣(17)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"c1657ed07df08e9638a110dbdeac5c4bccddf1cc","tid":418594,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:47:23.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/391410/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/391410/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃第一圈抽籤結果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/390687\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/390687</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃分組賽抽籤結果"},{"pid":"e154f6e863b65c473e668ea7ec7bbece0823a02f","tid":418594,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02cbca2c663fc27bf0536b2b73c780d1ea68fa2","tid":418594,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"票已投"},{"pid":"4ef5a9fd111c998c0bc0e9d75150a6ce1376fb14","tid":418594,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:13:43.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好誤會,雖然我依家都覺得ar moon張相真係好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我絕對無逼害過佢<br />\n因為我搵左好耐,符合參賽要求即係端莊唔扮可愛又或者P圖過度的相片<br />\n最好就係呢張,如果最後因為咁而令佢全季輸晒0分出局<br />\n我表示十分遺憾,但我重申<br />\n本會十分公平,絕無逼害劉佩玥既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd1f720e362ebb6e044fbb695d95b28c1fe1fd7","tid":418594,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24df05609d0faaa4506bb0cc8b8bd98b5d43e29","tid":418594,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T20:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0476860d0586585c7e99ef3e69cd908d32d0a2bf","tid":418594,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T23:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cd013956bf3c7dcb498972b04d5924b0427053","tid":418594,"uid":43619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:44:36.000Z","msg":"雪雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a298578393a5bbd2b98d36c4fc63b7c5f5ffd169","tid":418594,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"